Hello all the hosts and guests here. 

My name is Oton, and I believe that responsibility and trustworthiness are the cornerstones of any great relationship, whether it's in hosting or being a guest.

I've always prided myself on being someone others can rely on. Whether it's keeping commitments, taking care of details, or simply being there when needed, I strive to be a dependable presence in the lives of those around me.

In terms of my background, I have a passion for travel that has taken me to some incredible places. One of my favorite travel experiences was backpacking through Florida. The sights, sounds, and flavors of different Florida landscapings left an indelible mark on me. 

When I'm not on the road, I enjoy a variety of hobbies. I'm an avid reader, finding solace in the pages of a good book. I'm also a bit of a foodie, always on the lookout for new recipes to try and restaurants to explore. Whether it's hiking in the great outdoors or cozying up with a movie at home, I find joy in the simple pleasures of life.


If you'd like to connect further, you can find me on Twitter @ogftravel (X.com/ogftravel)  and on Facebook at facebook.com/ogftravel . Feel free to reach out.
